deal_title: Portronics Mport 31 Plus USB 3.0 Hub (5-in-1) with USB & Type-C Dual Plugs, Upto 5 Gbps High Speed, USB 3.0, 2-Port USB 2.0 & SD/microSD Card Reader for Laptop, PC, Mac, Smartphone, Tablet (Grey)
product_description: Introducing the Portronics Mport 31 Plus, a 5-in-1 USB Hub. This versatile hub offers seamless multitasking with a USB 3.0 port, 2 USB 2.0 ports, an SD Card Reader, and a MicroSD Card Reader. Experience fast data transfers of up to 5 Gbps in the USB 3.0 port and 480 Mbps in the USB 2.0 ports, perfect for connecting various devices. It offers dedicated slots for microSD and SD cards. With USB-A and USB-C plugs, it is compatible with PCs, Macs, Smartphones, and Tablets. Its durable aluminium alloy body, and compact design, ensure portability wherever you go.
